      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant should be a student.\n1. The student should engage in research/pursue Engineering Graduate &amp; Postgraduate Degrees/Ph.D. students in Renewable Energy/CA/CA(Inter)/CS/ICWA/ICWA(Inter)/CMA students/MBA students in HR/Finance/IT/CC from recognized institutions in India or abroad.\n1. The applicant must have his own laptop for the internship. \n1. The applicant must maintain a regular schedule and demonstrate professionalism. \n1. The applicant must sign a non-disclosure agreement to protect SECI&#39;s data.\n\n<br>\n\n**NOTE:** SECI shall provide them with working space, internet facility, and other necessities as deemed fit by the concerned Heads. However, CA/CA(Inter)/CS/ICWA/ICWA(Inter)CMA/MBA interns may be provided the desktop as per the requirement.\n",
